1. What is this Technology?
Data Analytics is the process of collecting, cleaning, analyzing, and visualizing data to identify patterns and support business decisions.
Data Science is a broader field that combines statistics, programming, machine learning, and domain knowledge to extract insights and build predictive models from data

2. Where is it Used?
Healthcare – Patient diagnosis and treatment analysis
Finance – Fraud detection and risk analysis
E-commerce – Customer behavior analysis and recommendations
Marketing – Campaign performance tracking
Manufacturing – Quality control and predictive maintenance
Education – Student performance analysis
Government – Policy and public service analysis

