5. Future Scope
Growing demand across all industries.
AI and Machine Learning are increasing the need for data professionals.
Organizations rely on data-driven decision-making.
High salary potential and global opportunities.
Strong career growth in Analytics, AI, and Data Science.

Conclusion
Data Analytics and Data Science are among the fastest-growing technologies today. 
They help organizations make informed decisions, improve efficiency, and drive innovation using data. 
With the rise of AI, the future demand for skilled data professionals will continue to increase.

